name: Akiza Izinski (Yu-Gi-Oh!) LoRA
description:
General Info

This LoRa has been trained using the Fruitmix Model i uploaded before and has the capability of generating character portrait art that very closely resembles Akiza Izinski from Yu-Gi-Oh 5D's. This is my first ever try at creating a LoRA and there will be an improved model in the near future.

Usage

The model has been trained using Kohya so you probably want to use it in the same way as you use other Kohya models. If you are Using A1111's Webui you want to move the file into the models>Lora directory.
